snippet.title: Grand Theft Auto: Terminator 2 "Judgment Game" HD
snippet.description:
A GTA San Andreas MOD - TERMINATOR 2 - Gameplay (T2: Judgment Day)

This gameplay includes first and second part combined for this "judgment game" GTASA mod!

This is a Terminator 2 Judgment Day mod for Grand Theft Auto San Andreas. All Credits go to ~~FAPSAMUP~~ Samuel Faict
